data.description:
Don't miss this beautifully remodeled Townhome and step into a world of modern elegance where every detail has been carefully curated for an exquisite living experience. This stunning residence boasts a complete overhaul. Revel in the luxuriously renovated interiors with all-new cabinets, granite countertops. The designer's touch is evident throughout, from the doors, hardware, and base trim to the tastefully chosen designer paint that enhances the contemporary vibe. The transformation doesn't stop there. Picture-perfect bathrooms, a sleek kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances Nestled in an enviable location, this home offers the best of Scottsdale living. Enjoy direct access to the Silverado Golf Course and the picturesque Hayden Greenbelt path for leisurely strolls. Indulge in nearby shopping options at Hilton Village and Fashion Square, while education opportunities abound with Saguaro High School and Scottsdale Community College just moments away. Relish in the heated community pool, providing a serene escape and a perfect gathering spot for relaxation and recreation.

This home is truly move-in ready, offering an incredible price for the remarkable value it presents. Don't miss this opportunity to own a fully renovated haven in an unbeatable location. With its allure, superior upgrades, and prime setting, this home is a rare find. Act fast, as a property of this caliber won't stay on the market for long. Bring your clients to witness the undeniable charm of 6113 N. 79th St, Scottsdale, AZ 85250 before it's gone!
